                <supplied reason="lost">Primi</supplied>genius <del rend="erasure">[<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></del>] <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratoris</ex></expan> Ve</supplied>spasiani <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">procur</supplied>atoris a<supplied reason="lost">r</supplied>carius <lb n="4"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost">Matri</supplied> Deum ex im<supplied reason="lost">p</supplied>erio <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">eius</supplied> posuit
